OL,3,CThe Cammell Laird 37: Jailed strikers
OL,4,Cfight to clear their names
OL,6,FOutside of Merseyside, few people have
OL,7,Fheard the story of the Cammell Laird
OL,8,F37.
OL,10,FBut along the banks of the Mersey,
OL,11,Fthese former shipyard workers are
OL,12,Flegendary.
OL,14,FThey're also convicted criminals.
OL,16,F"I still can't believe that," former
OL,17,Fshipyard apprentice Allan Small
OL,18,Fremembers. "It was wrong then, and
OL,19,Fit's wrong now.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
