OL,3,CThe Cammell Laird 37: Jailed strikers
OL,4,Cfight to clear their names
OL,6,F"These lads weren't just fighting for
OL,7,Ftheir own jobs. They were fighting for
OL,8,Four jobs, our futures, and basically
OL,9,Fthe future of Birkenhead really.
OL,11,F"The shipyards they were fighting to
OL,12,Fsave were the biggest employers at the
OL,13,Ftime, they knew, once those jobs
OL,14,Fwent... well, you could see the impact
OL,15,Fit had on the town. The devastation.
OL,16,FYou can still see it today."
OL,18,FWho were the Cammell Laird 37?
