OL,3,CThe Cammell Laird 37: Jailed strikers
OL,4,Cfight to clear their names
OL,6,FKnowing the impact it would have on
OL,7,Fthe area, 37 workers staged a protest,
OL,8,Foccupying a partially built gas rig on
OL,9,Fthe sight, in a fight to save their
OL,10,Fjobs and their community.
OL,12,F"They knew, if they broke us, they'd
OL,13,Fbreak the other yards," said Billy
OL,14,FAlbertina, who led the occupation for
OL,15,Ffour months.
OL,17,F"First of all they started making it
OL,18,Fharder for us to get food on to the
OL,19,Fsite, so we had to start cutting down
OL,20,Fon that.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
