OL,3,CThe Cammell Laird 37: Jailed strikers
OL,4,Cfight to clear their names
OL,6,FWhat happened next?
OL,8,FThe 37 men were jailed for a month,
OL,9,Fbut the consequences lasted far
OL,10,Flonger: they were sacked, stripped of
OL,11,Fpensions, and blacklisted.
OL,13,FBilly Albertina - with his distinctive
OL,14,Fname - struggled to get other work.
OL,16,FBilly said: "When we came out of
OL,17,Fprison, I couldn't get a job.
OL,19,F"The name Albertina, there was only
OL,20,Fone family called Albertina and that
OL,21,Fwas ours.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
