OL,3,CThe Cammell Laird 37: Jailed strikers
OL,4,Cfight to clear their names
OL,6,FIn 2014 the European Parliament agreed
OL,7,Fthere was no legal basis for their
OL,8,Fimprisonment and urged the UK
OL,9,FGovernment to apologise and clear
OL,10,Ftheir names - something the men are
OL,11,Fstill fighting for a decade later.
OL,13,FBut time is not on their side.
OL,15,FFourteen of the 37 have already died,
OL,16,Fincluding Christopher Whitley, brother
OL,17,Fof the former Birkenhead MP Mick
OL,18,FWhitley.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
