OL,3,CThe Cammell Laird 37: Jailed strikers
OL,4,Cfight to clear their names
OL,6,FMick said: "We have had 40 years of
OL,7,Fpain and now's the time for this
OL,8,FLabour Government to say, enough's
OL,9,Fenough.
OL,11,F"If somebody else gets in power after
OL,12,Fthis term it's not going to happen. So
OL,13,Fit's got to happen in the next four
OL,14,Fyears."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
