OL,3,CThe Cammell Laird 37: Jailed strikers
OL,4,Cfight to clear their names
OL,6,FThat's why the Cammell Laird 37 are
OL,7,Fnow taking their call to Parliament,
OL,8,Fdemanding the government release all
OL,9,Frelevant documents and help them clear
OL,10,Ftheir names, fighting to undo what
OL,11,Fthey say has been four decades of
OL,12,Finjustice.
OL,14,FThey're being supported by Liverpool
OL,15,FMP Kim Johnson, who says there is "no
OL,16,Fdoubt" this is a major miscarriage of
OL,17,Fjustice.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
