OL,3,CThe Cammell Laird 37: Jailed strikers
OL,4,Cfight to clear their names
OL,6,FIn response to the campaign, a
OL,7,FGovernment spokesperson said: "We
OL,8,Frecognise this is an incredibly
OL,9,Fdifficult case for all concerned, and
OL,10,Ffor the local community more broadly,
OL,11,Fwith long-lasting impacts on those
OL,12,Faffected.
OL,14,F"The ability to strike is an important
OL,15,Fpart of industrial relations in the
OL,16,FUK, rightly protected by law."
